Module com.example.project3rubank
Package com.example.project3rubank.bank

Class AccountNumber

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3rubank.bank.AccountNumber
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<AccountNumber>
public class AccountNumber extends Object implements Comparable<AccountNumber>
The AccountNumber class represents a unique account identifier that contains a branch code, an account type and a randomly generated 4-digit number. It implements comparable for sorting purposes and comparison purposes using the 9-digit account number.
